86
00:03:33.855 --> 00:03:34.655
Veamos.

87
00:03:35.135 --> 00:03:36.095
¿Por qué?

88
00:03:36.575 --> 00:03:39.375
Se me ha contratado, señor Paul, sistema de

89
00:03:39.375 --> 00:03:41.055
