199
00:07:50.020 --> 00:07:50.900
Primer punto.

200
00:07:51.505 --> 00:07:52.385
Ahora,

201
00:07:52.545 --> 00:07:53.345
segundo.

202
00:07:53.905 --> 00:07:56.545
Ustedes traen 4 personas

203
00:07:56.625 --> 00:07:59.025
