204
00:07:59.025 --> 00:07:59.665
que,

205
00:07:59.825 --> 00:08:01.265
según he oído,

206
00:08:01.425 --> 00:08:05.185
van á tener sus dormitorios approa con

207
00:08:05.185 --> 00:08:06.545
