212
00:08:14.360 --> 00:08:15.800
¿Hay algo más?

213
00:08:16.440 --> 00:08:18.680
Preguntó el señor Trilogni.

214
00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:19.560
Sí,

215
00:08:19.800 --> 00:08:22.120
